        Question constructor. Date is created at time of creation. This question will add a location to the question object.
        Parameters:
        title - String will be set as title/
        body - String will be set as body.
        image - Image to be set in the body of the image. Not yet implemented. Null.
        author - Username of the author will be set as author of the question.
        location - simple location object containing coordinates
        locationName - simple location string containing name of location
